# --- Local agent / editor context (mostly not shared) ---
CLAUDE.md
# Ignore .claude/ contents, but DO share the Sage/Nova/Vera persona system:
# the slash commands and the handoff workflow README. Transient session
# artifacts (current-brief, build-log, build-complete, review-result,
# session-checkpoint) stay local.
.claude/*
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/handoff/
.claude/handoff/*
!.claude/handoff/README.md

# --- Secrets / local env ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key

